<item>
            <title>[LU-1255] recovery-mds-scale FAIL: rundbench: no client file found for dbench DBENCH_LIB= SRC=</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1255</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This is a test script/configuration issue while running recovery-*-scale tests on RHEL5 or SLES11 client. The dbench load description file is installed in &quot;/usr/share/doc/dbench/loadfiles&quot;, which is not in the default search path in rundbench script. Although we specified DBENCH_LIB=&quot;/usr/share/doc/dbench/loadfiles&quot; to the test script, the value of this variable was not passed to run_dbench.sh in start_client_load().&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Running recovery-*-scale tests on RHEL6 client did not hit this issue because the dbench load file was installed in &quot;/usr/share/dbench&quot;, which was in the default search path in rundbench script.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Maloo reports:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/c67f2f88-7473-11e1-b427-5254004bbbd3&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/c67f2f88-7473-11e1-b427-5254004bbbd3&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/d1affc0c-7473-11e1-b427-5254004bbbd3&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/d1affc0c-7473-11e1-b427-5254004bbbd3&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/19fbc388-7474-11e1-b427-5254004bbbd3&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/19fbc388-7474-11e1-b427-5254004bbbd3&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
